  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>This hotel is suite for both business and leisure travelers. Fitness centre and swimming pool is on rooftop of hotel. Spa facilities are also available for customer's choice. (01/09SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>Hotel is located in between Silom and Sathorn Road, Bangkok's most vibrant commercial business district and shopping area. It is just only a minute walk from Chongnonsi sky train station.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Deluxe room size is 26 square meters, located only on 7th and 8th floor. Room is decorated in modern and colorful style. LCD TV screen, hair dryer, safety box refridgerator, mini bar, coffee and tea facilities are included in room. Guests can access free of charge internet access by LAN in room or wireless internet at lobby area. Bathroom is with bathtub.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is a high-rise building with 9 floors, constructed with white concrete and glass.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>There is only one restaurant, on ground floor back behind the lobby area.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>Lobby is a medium size with modern decoration. Limited colorful sofa seats. Internet corner is available and free access. Lobby bar is next to reception area.</Text>
  </Description>
